news.title: Maharashtra govt to study suggestions on doing away with NA tax for societies
news.para: Additional chief secretary (revenue) Nitin Kareer said that the issue was still “under consideration”. He told TOI on Wednesday that the data was being analysed and options will be presented to the government soon.

news.title: Goa hikes stamp duty for transfer of property registration
news.para: The revenue department said that it aims to “reduce the stamp duty chargeable on conveyance”, but the conveyance charges have actually become more expensive, said builders.

news.title: Gurugram: Fire officials took bribe to certify five towers of Orris Aster Court Premier as safe
news.para: The MCG began the probe after a group of residents of the society approached the chief minister with a complaint against then assistant divisional fire officer (ADFO) Satyawan Samriwal in June last year.
